When to Use Tuple?

When data should NOT change

Faster than list

Used in coordinates, fixed values

2ï¸âƒ£ Sets
What is a Set?

A set is:

Unordered

No duplicate values allowed

Syntax
numbers = {10, 20, 30}

Important Property (No Duplicates)
numbers = {10, 20, 20, 30}
print(numbers)


âœ… Output:

{10, 20, 30}


Duplicate removed automatically.

Add & Remove in Set
numbers.add(40)
numbers.remove(20)

